tag_irrelevant:
theorem tag_irrelevant {a : α} (h1 h2 : p a) : mk a h1 = mk a h2 :=
  rfl
#align tag_irrelevant tag_irrelevant
ne_of_val_ne:
theorem ne_of_val_ne {a1 a2 : { x // p x }} : val a1 ≠ val a2 → a1 ≠ a2 :=
  mt <| congr_arg _
#align ne_of_val_ne ne_of_val_ne
exists_of_subtype:

theorem exists_of_subtype {α : Type u} {p : α → Prop} : { x // p x } → ∃ x, p x
  | ⟨a, h⟩ => ⟨a, h⟩
#align exists_of_subtype exists_of_subtype
eta:
theorem eta (a : { x // p x }) (h : p (val a)) : mk (val a) h = a :=
  subtype.eq rfl
#align eta eta
eq:
protected theorem eq : ∀ {a1 a2 : { x // p x }}, val a1 = val a2 → a1 = a2
  | ⟨x, h1⟩, ⟨x, h2⟩, rfl => rfl
#align eq eq
